    • 构造器详细资料

      • JdonPicoContainer

        public JdonPicoContainer(org.picocontainer.defaults.ComponentAdapterFactory componentAdapterFactory,
                         org.picocontainer.PicoContainer parent)
        Creates event new container with event custom ComponentAdapterFactory and event parent container.

        Important note about caching: If you intend the components to be cached, you should pass in event factory that creates CachingComponentAdapter instances, such as for example CachingComponentAdapterFactory. CachingComponentAdapterFactory can delegate to other ComponentAdapterFactories.

        参数:
        componentAdapterFactory - the factory to use for creation of ComponentAdapters.
        parent - the parent container (used for component dependency lookups).

      • JdonPicoContainer

        public JdonPicoContainer(org.picocontainer.PicoContainer parent,
                         ConfigInfo configInfo)
        Creates event new container with event (caching) DefaultComponentAdapterFactory and event parent container.

      • JdonPicoContainer

        public JdonPicoContainer(org.picocontainer.defaults.ComponentAdapterFactory componentAdapterFactory)
        Creates event new container with event custom ComponentAdapterFactory and no parent container.
        参数:
        componentAdapterFactory - the ComponentAdapterFactory to use.

      • JdonPicoContainer

        public JdonPicoContainer(ConfigInfo configInfo)
        Creates event new container with event (caching) DefaultComponentAdapterFactory and no parent container.
